  "original_poem": "तुरेल नुपा यम्लैक्ख्रिबा,  \nसाना चंगु मगनुंगली,  \nनोनी नारानबाशिगी,  \nयुंबिनु मग्नुम ओक्ते।\n\nलामंग थावंग थमाइब,  \nनिंगोल सिंगनबाउबा,  \nइयेंगुं तुंबाई ओइ,  \nताम्बा मोयोम इमो ओई।",
  "translated_poem": "The river, a man restless and bold,  \nCarving the earth with stories untold,  \nDancing with the grace of the night,  \nWeaving through villages, out of sight.\n\nThe hills bow as he roars ahead,  \nCarrying dreams in his riverbed,  \nWhispers of love from mountain’s breast,  \nThe river flows on, never to rest.",
